### Login (obtener token)
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "student",
  "password": "student123"
}

### Listar blueprints (usar token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/blueprints
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Obtener blueprints por autor
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/blueprints/JohnConnor
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Obtener blueprint espec√≠fico
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/blueprints/JohnConnor/MyHouse
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Crear nuevo blueprint
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/blueprints
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "author": "TestAuthor",
  "name": "TestBlueprint",
  "points": [
    {"x": 10, "y": 20},
    {"x": 30, "y": 40}
  ]
}

### Actualizar blueprint existente
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/blueprints/TestAuthor/TestBlueprint
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "author": "TestAuthor",
  "name": "UpdatedBlueprint",
  "points": [
    {"x": 15, "y": 25},
    {"x": 35, "y": 45},
    {"x": 50, "y": 60}
  ]
}

### Eliminar blueprint
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/blueprints/TestAuthor/UpdatedBlueprint
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
